{
  "texts": [
    "As the study suggests, GAI has the capacity to take on substantial portions of tasks traditionally handled by educators.",
    "This shift in responsibilities could lead to educators van den Berg Open Praxis DOI: 10.55982/ openpraxis.16.2.640",
    "using GAI as a supporting partner to be more efficient, allowing them more time to focus on teaching and interacting with their students.",
    "Therefore, the implication is not that GAI should or will replace the crucial role educators play in their teaching, as this study has confirmed.",
    "This study explored how a specific group of educators partner with GAI AI tools in their teaching and how it transforms education."
  ]
}